dcterms:description: A synthetic dataset with simple grammar rules, consisting of sequences alternating between 'x' and operators (+, -, *, /). Two training sets of size 10,000 were created with sequence lengths of 3 and 15.
dcterms:title: Synthetic Grammar Dataset
